Terraform – Usage, Best Practices, Drift

20. What is your experience with Terraform? How much have you worked on it?


21. What steps do you follow to make Terraform enterprise-ready?


22. Are you using Terraform Enterprise or open-source?


23. What is this TOFU version of Terraform? Explain.


24. Why do you run Terraform locally on VMs instead of integrating with CI/CD?


25. Where is your Terraform state file stored?


26. If the state file contains cloud passwords and secrets, is storing it in GitLab a good practice? Why?


27. If someone creates or deletes resources manually from the cloud console, what happens when you run Terraform apply?


28. What are the best practices you follow for Terraform drift management?


29. Have you ever encountered a drift issue and how did you fix it?




