Observability / Monitoring / AppDynamics / OpenTelemetry

30. I see on your resume that you configured Hazelcast with OpenTelemetry and AppDynamics — can you walk us through how you configured it?


31. Is the instrumentation Auto-instrumentation or Manual-instrumentation?


32. If there are 5 applications to onboard to AppDynamics, how do you onboard them? Is it manual or automated?


33. What does your automation pipeline for AppDynamics onboarding do?


34. If one application is Java and another is .NET, will the APD agent be the same or different? Why?


35. Is AppDynamics agent push-based or pull-based?


36. Are you only responsible for installing agents, or also for configuring monitoring, alerting, dashboards?


37. Can you share one incident where AppDynamics helped you diagnose an issue and how you troubleshot it?


38. What is the core strength of AppDynamics? Why do we use it?




